            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Numerius <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Vel</abbr><ex>ina</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Rufus <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>patron</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>portic</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>reficiund</abbr><ex>am</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>de sua <expan><abbr>pecun</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coer</abbr><ex>avit</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>idemque <expan><abbr>prob</abbr><ex>avit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: Q. Numerius Rufus Volkstribun war 57 v. Chr. tribunus plebis und vermutlich circa 55 v. Chr. Legat.</p>
            </div>
